## Max-FPS Env Var Reference

### Always-on for ALL Adreno/Turnip games (applied globally in `applyIsolationEnv`):
| Variable | Value | Effect |
|----------|-------|--------|
| `TU_DEBUG` | `noconform` | Skip Turnip conformance tests — reduces GPU init time |
| `mesa_glthread` | `true` | Mesa GL threading — offloads CPU-side GL work |
| `MESA_NO_ERROR` | `1` | Skip GL error checking in Mesa — saves CPU per-call |
| `MESA_SHADER_CACHE_MAX_SIZE` | `512MB` | Persistent ISA-level cache — zero shader recompile on relaunch |
| `DXVK_GPLASYNCCACHE` | `1` | GPU-side async pipeline cache — companion to DXVK_ASYNC |

### Per-game performance boosters (put in `KnownGameFixes.extraEnvVars`):
| Variable | Value | Use Case |
|----------|-------|----------|
| `DXVK_ASYNC` | `1` | ALL DX9/10/11 games — prevent render thread shader stall |
| `PULSE_LATENCY_MSEC` | `60` | Games with XAudio2 audio hang at startup |
| `WINEDLLOVERRIDES` | `mfplat.dll=n,b;xaudio2_7.dll=n,b` | Games that hang playing intro videos |
| `PROTON_ENABLE_NVAPI` | `0` | ALL DX12 games — disable NVAPI CPU waste |
| `VKD3D_CONFIG` | `pipeline_library_app_cache,no_upload_hvv,force_static_cbv` | ALL DX12 games |

### Never do:
- Do NOT set `WINEDEBUG` to anything other than `-all` in production (kills 5–10% CPU)
- Do NOT set `DXVK_HUD` in production builds
- Do NOT set `strict_shader_math=1` in DXVK config for DX9/DX11 games on Adreno — causes incorrect shader output
- Do NOT use `forceUseLegacyDrm=true` for games where `ColdClientLoader` works — only for Aspyr/sub-launcher titles

---

## `forceUseLegacyDrm` — When and Why

Use **only** for games where `ColdClientLoader` (the Goldberg launcher) silently fails to `CreateProcess` the actual game exe. Symptoms:
- Wine log shows `wfm.exe` starting but NOT the game exe
- No `init_peb` line for the expected `.exe`
- Typically Aspyr ports (UE3 titles), games with sub-launchers

**Required fields when `forceUseLegacyDrm = true`:**
```kotlin
forceUseLegacyDrm = true,
gameExePath = "relative/path/to/Game.exe",  // from game install dir, forward-slashes
```
Goldberg `steam_api64.dll` is replaced in-game dir via `MainViewModel.replaceSteamApi()`.

