## ProtonVersion Selection Guide

| ProtonDB Tier | Default | Notes |
|--------------|---------|-------|
| Platinum | 10.0 | Latest works fine |
| Gold | 9.0 | Safer — many Gold games have 10.0 regressions |
| Silver | 8.0 | Stick with stable 8.0 |
| Bronze | 8.0 | High crash risk — try Compatibility preset |
| Borked | Wine-GE | Last resort |

**Override in KnownGameFixes** when a specific game is known to work better on a different version.
